astreainfinitum.gui.knowledge.tablet.text=By reading tablets that were lost many millennium ago, you start to understand ancient practices that were thought to have been lost. You get the idea of combining 4 mana drops with a book in a crafting table...
astreainfinitum.gui.book.basic.text=Welcome to the world of magic. Magic has always been around but only a select few could actually utilize it, with all of this modern technology people forgot about the art of magic so unfortunately it died out, although people forgot about it, it didn't mean that the magic itself went away, it has been lying dormant around us, collecting power... Waiting until someone wakes it up. 